name: Sylvie Ringer - Ceramic mural plate 50 cm diameter
description:
Ceramic mural plate - 50 cm diameter
Hand-painted by Sylvie Ringer
Made in 2012 during the project PESO ALLE IMMAGINI in the "Solimene Art " lab, in Cava de' Tirreni, Italy.

Sylvie Ringer was born in Kamloops in Canada in 1983. She attended the HAW Hamburg (Hamburg University of Applied Sciences) She participated in various group exhibitions in Europe and in Japan. She is actively running a screen printing workshop in Hamburg where she lives and works.

www.sylvieringer.blogspot.com

www.pesoalleimmagini.blogspot.com

name: Anna Deflorian - Ceramic mural plate 50 cm diameter
description:
Ceramic mural plate -  50 cm diameter
Hand-painted by Anna Deflorian
Made in 2012 during the project PESO ALLE IMMAGINI in the "Solimene Art " lab, in Cava de' Tirreni, Italy.

Anna Deflorian was born in Trento in 1985. She studied illustration in Bologna and Hamburg. She collaborates with Canicola editions of Bologna. Her works are published in Italy by Canicola, Teiera, and abroad by Kuš! (LV), Kuti (FI), Mami Verlag (D), Na! Editions (F), Kabinett (A).

www.annadeflorian.com

www.pesoalleimmagini.blogspot.com

name: Lilli Gärtner - Ceramic mural plate 50 cm diameter
description:
Ceramic mural plate -  50 cm diameter
Hand-painted by Lilli Gärtner
Made in 2012 during the project PESO ALLE IMMAGINI in the "Solimene Art " lab, in Cava de' Tirreni, Italy.

Lilli Gärtner was born in Tübingen, South Germany, in 1980. She lived in Canterbury (UK), Berlin, Baltimore (USA) and Hamburg, where she studied Drawing (University of Fine Arts) and Illustration (Hamburg University of Applied Sciences). Now she lives and works as an illustrator in Leipzig,Germany. 

www.lilligaertner.de
